---
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
import Eyebrow from '../ui/Eyebrow.astro';
---

<Section bg="bg-ink" class="flex flex-col gap-10 py-20 lg:py-24">
  <Eyebrow>Por qué Stride</Eyebrow>

  <blockquote
    class="max-w-[1000px] text-[28px] font-medium leading-[1.28] tracking-[-1px] text-bg sm:text-[32px] lg:text-[38px]"
  >
    Cambiamos cinco herramientas por una. Ahora las decisiones de producto
    tardan horas, no semanas.
  </blockquote>

  <figcaption class="flex items-center gap-3.5 pt-2">
    <span
      class="flex h-[46px] w-[46px] items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent font-mono text-[15px] font-semibold text-on-accent"
    >
      MV
    </span>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5">
      <span class="text-[15px] font-semibold text-bg">Mara Vintilă</span>
      <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-ink-3">VP de Producto · Köld</span>
    </div>
  </figcaption>
</Section>
